name: Wall Art-50 butterflies
description:
50 butterflies in 5 sizes and 5 colours
suitable for internal or external use (5yrs external)

Transform you Home with this simple to install wall art stickers.

SIZE GUIDE

stuck end to end approx 2.5m

Made from high grade quality vinyl and professionally cut using state of art equipment.

Add some elegance to your lounge, bedroom, dining room, kitchen or workplace.

This vinyl decal is also suitable for your car, windows or any flat surface. It will last a lifetime indoors and is guaranteed for 5-7 years externally

 

This Item is Brand New
We DO NOT accept returns unless the item is damaged or not as described
If you are not happy with your chosen product, contact us and we will do everything we can to help.
When returning items to us, please place your returned goods in their original packaging and do not remove any labels or tags.
 
Stickers & Decals
How To Apply
Clean and dry surface
Tape in position
Remove backing sheet
Lay sticker in desired position and rub over from the center outwards with a storecard/credit card
Slowly remove the application tape (clear) making sure all of the sticker has adheared to the surface
Rub over the sticker GENTLY with your finger or card to ensure 100% adheasion
